docs-site\docs\release\version-log.md:92: - 用余额生成礼品卡改用独立 `gift_card_issue` 余额日志类型，不再计入可兑换积分的真实消费额。
docs-site\docs\release\version-log.md:93: - 新增历史日志重分类迁移，使用礼品卡关联、金额与事务时间窗口识别历史发行扣款。
docs-site\docs\release\version-log.md:714: - 提交说明 / Commit subject: Release v1.0.6 flash sale editing
docs-site\docs\release\version-log.md:716: - Allow admins to edit generated flash sale campaign content and time windows.
docs-site\docs\release\version-log.md:718: - Allow admins to edit flash sale item price, stock, per-user limit, coupon and AFF settings.
docs-site\docs\release\version-log.md:722: - Add guard coverage for generated flash sale editing.
docs-site\docs\release\version-log.md:728: - 提交说明 / Commit subject: Release v1.0.5 flash sales
docs-site\docs\release\version-log.md:730: - Add flash sale campaigns, items, reservations, stock audit and guarded admin/user APIs.
docs-site\docs\release\version-log.md:732: - Add user flash sale page and admin multi-item flash sale management.
docs-site\docs\release\version-log.md:734: - Route flash sale purchases through the normal instance billing, Turnstile, risk restriction, stock lock and delivery compensation chain.
docs-site\docs\release\version-log.md:736: - Add flash sale guard coverage and documentation.
docs-site\docs\release\version-log.md:1102: - Improve gift card user/admin UI safety, code masking, copy, and responsive layout.
docs-site\docs\release\version-log.md:1110: - 提交说明 / Commit subject: Fix gift card Turnstile body verification
docs-site\docs\release\version-log.md:1114: - Move user gift card Turnstile verification from onRequest to preHandler so body turnstileToken is available.
docs-site\docs\release\version-log.md:1124: - 提交说明 / Commit subject: Persist expired gift card state
docs-site\docs\release\version-log.md:1128: - Persist expired gift card state `e67c9603f`
docs-site\docs\release\version-log.md:1134: - 提交说明 / Commit subject: Fix gift card Turnstile token flow
docs-site\docs\release\version-log.md:1138: - Fix gift card Turnstile token flow `d0389797f`
docs-site\docs\release\version-log.md:1144: - 提交说明 / Commit subject: Fix user gift card Turnstile verification
docs-site\docs\release\version-log.md:1148: - Fix user gift card Turnstile verification `dae1a64c5`
docs-site\docs\release\version-log.md:1154: - 提交说明 / Commit subject: Fix admin gift card generation Turnstile gate
docs-site\docs\release\version-log.md:1158: - Fix admin gift card generation Turnstile gate `2fcc75bfb`
docs-site\docs\release\version-log.md:1174: - 提交说明 / Commit subject: Add gift card center
docs-site\docs\release\version-log.md:1178: - Add user gift card page for balance-funded gift card generation, redemption, and owned-card history.
docs-site\docs\release\version-log.md:1180: - Add admin gift card center for single and batch generation, stats, redacted lists, enable, disable, and delete actions.
docs-site\docs\release\version-log.md:1186: - Protect gift card balance flows with advisory locks, transaction-scoped balance deduction, self-redeem blocking, and one-time redeem claims.
docs-site\docs\release\version-log.md:1188: - Restrict production gift card management with PAYINCUS_GIFT_CARD_ADMIN_IDS and mask codes by default.
docs-site\docs\release\version-log.md:1585: - 后台日志页新增风险审计概览，显示风险动作数量、本页高风险、需要审批和需要验证码的记录数。 / Added an audit summary to the admin logs page with risk catalog count, high-risk records, approval-required records, and verification-required records.
docs-site\docs\release\version-log.md:1589: - 新增高风险操作目录，覆盖系统更新、支付通道、余额调账、批量删除实例、节点、套餐、管理员权限和插件安装等动作。 / Added a high-risk operation catalog covering system updates, payment providers, balance adjustments, batch instance deletion, hosts, packages, admin role changes, and plugin installation.
