docs-site\docs\en\release\version-log.md:1190: - Restrict production gift card management with PAYINCUS_GIFT_CARD_ADMIN_IDS and mask codes by default.
docs-site\docs\en\release\version-log.md:1587: - 后台日志页新增风险审计概览，显示风险动作数量、本页高风险、需要审批和需要验证码的记录数。 / Added an audit summary to the admin logs page with risk catalog count, high-risk records, approval-required records, and verification-required records.
docs-site\docs\en\release\version-log.md:1591: - 新增高风险操作目录，覆盖系统更新、支付通道、余额调账、批量删除实例、节点、套餐、管理员权限和插件安装等动作。 / Added a high-risk operation catalog covering system updates, payment providers, balance adjustments, batch instance deletion, hosts, packages, admin role changes, and plugin installation.
docs-site\docs\en\user\dashboard.md:22: | Flash Sales | `/flash-sales` | Shows limited-time campaigns, stock, flash prices and the current user's purchase records, then routes eligible purchases into the normal instance creation, billing and delivery chain. |
docs-site\docs\en\user\dashboard.md:29: | Gift Cards | `/gift-cards` | Generate gift cards from the user's own balance, redeem cards issued by others or admins, and view owned cards. |
docs-site\docs\en\user\dashboard.md:46: ## Gift Cards
docs-site\docs\en\user\dashboard.md:48: Users can generate gift cards from their own balance and redeem cards issued by other users or administrators. Self-redemption is blocked, and balance deduction, card creation, redemption and ledger writes are handled transactionally by the backend.
docs-site\docs\features\billing.md:15: | 礼品卡 | 在 `/gift-cards` 使用余额生成礼品卡、兑换他人或后台发放的礼品卡，并查看自己的礼品卡记录。 |
docs-site\docs\features\billing.md:16: | 兑换码 | 使用管理员发放的兑换码增加余额或权益。 |
docs-site\docs\features\billing.md:32: | 礼品卡 | 在 `/admin/gift-cards` 单张或批量生成礼品卡，查看统计和脱敏列表，并启用、禁用或删除未使用礼品卡。 |
docs-site\docs\features\billing.md:33: | 兑换码 | 创建、禁用、使用记录和库存管理。 |
docs-site\docs\features\billing.md:57: - `gift-cards`：礼品卡生成、兑换、余额锁、脱敏列表和后台管理。
docs-site\docs\features\billing.md:61: - `redeem-codes`：兑换码。
docs-site\docs\features\billing.md:71: - 礼品卡属于余额类高风险能力，生产必须配置 `PAYINCUS_GIFT_CARD_ADMIN_IDS`，用户余额生成和兑换必须保持事务一致，后台列表默认脱敏。
docs-site\docs\features\billing.md:88: - 礼品卡用户余额生成会扣减余额并写入余额流水；兑换不能自兑，重复并发兑换只能成功一次。
docs-site\docs\features\billing.md:89: - 后台礼品卡管理在生产未配置 `PAYINCUS_GIFT_CARD_ADMIN_IDS` 时拒绝访问，配置后列表默认脱敏。
docs-site\docs\guide\architecture.md:31: | 用户端 | `client/src` + `VITE_APP_ENTRY=user` | 用户登录、实例、终端、钱包、工单、通知、礼品卡和自助页面 |
docs-site\docs\guide\architecture.md:50: - PostgreSQL 保存用户、实例、套餐、账务、支付、礼品卡、工单、通知、日志、扩展、主题、Public API/OAuth 和系统更新任务。
docs-site\docs\guide\capability-matrix.md:21: | 礼品卡 | 已闭环 | `/admin/gift-cards` | `/gift-cards` | `server/src/routes/gift-cards.ts` | 已覆盖生成、兑换、白名单和 Turnstile；生产仍需配置对应管理员白名单和验证密钥。 |
