docs-site\docs\en\release\version-log.md:1180: - Add user gift card page for balance-funded gift card generation, redemption, and owned-card history.
docs-site\docs\en\release\version-log.md:1182: - Add admin gift card center for single and batch generation, stats, redacted lists, enable, disable, and delete actions.
docs-site\docs\en\release\version-log.md:1188: - Protect gift card balance flows with advisory locks, transaction-scoped balance deduction, self-redeem blocking, and one-time redeem claims.
docs-site\docs\en\release\version-log.md:1190: - Restrict production gift card management with PAYINCUS_GIFT_CARD_ADMIN_IDS and mask codes by default.
